Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 Stuart 新規矩\N{\fs20}Ok, Stuart, new ground rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 每當我有朋友過來\N{\fs20}From now on, whenever I have friends over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不能帶女孩兒回家\N{\fs20}you cannot bring a girl home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧 那才是第一次約會\N{\fs20}Give me a break. It was a first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感覺挺別扭的\N{\fs20}I was feeling uncomfortable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然別扭了 \N{\fs20}Of course, you were feeling uncomfortable. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她張開四肢扒在你身上\N{\fs20}She rode you in on all fours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這得怪我\N{\fs20}That was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太調皮了\N{\fs20}I had been very naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫個忙好嗎\N{\fs20}Do you guys mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作可是我一生的夢想\N{\fs20}It's been a lifelong dream of mine to do real writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終于能有機會寫一些東西\N{\fs20}I've finally been commissioned to do a piece
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投稿給全國聞名的雜志社\N{\fs20}for a respected national magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么 <紐約客>還是<名利場>\N{\fs20}Oh, really? The new yorker? Vanity fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<輕狂>\N{\fs20}Sassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就是截稿日了\N{\fs20}Any way, the article was due yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能靜一靜 各位\N{\fs20}so if I could get some peace and quiet, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然在約會的事兒上找我麻煩\N{\fs20}Can't believe you'd hassle me over a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我就從來都不抱怨\N{\fs20}You don't see me complaining
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你的狗咬我的床柱\N{\fs20}that dog chewed up my bedpost last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stuart昨晚Rags一直在獸醫那兒\N{\fs20}Stuart, Rags spent the night in the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得給那妞回電話\N{\fs20}I've gotta call that girl back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真輕狂\N{\fs20}She-e-e-e's sassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了\N{\fs20}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長 你今天的安排很緊\N{\fs20}Sir, you've got a full day ahead of ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9:00到10:45預算會議\N{\fs20}We start with a budget meeting from 9:00 to 10:45,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊挨著就是空氣質量管理的研討會\N{\fs20}rocket into a symposium on air quality management,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你以為自己不能再亢奮下去時 嘣\N{\fs20}and when you think you can't take any more excitement, bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有四個多小時的預算會議\N{\fs20}4 more hours of budget meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有沒有告訴你們我爺爺去世了\N{\fs20}Did I tell you guys that my grandfather died?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚嗎\N{\fs20}Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年前\N{\fs20}30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這讓我想到\N{\fs20}But it got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一生花了太多精力在工作上\N{\fs20}So much of our lives are spent focused on work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從不停下腳步\N{\fs20}We never stop and connect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那些人生中重要的人相處下\N{\fs20}with the people who are truly important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸的電話\N{\fs20}Sir, your dad's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說我不在\N{\fs20}I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們稍微停一停 來談談我們的\N{\fs20}Let's take a minute and let's talk about our...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人生活\N{\fs20}Personal lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paul 就從你開始吧\N{\fs20}Paul! Get us started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精子沒有活性\N{\fs20}I have non-motile sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天 還有30秒Doug的觀光團就要到了\N{\fs20}Oh, God. T-minus 30 seconds to tour guide Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 裝做我男朋友吧\N{\fs20}Carter, act like my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒時間\N{\fs20}Oh, sorry. I don't have time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買輛科邁羅然后再疏遠你的父母\N{\fs20}to buy a camaro and alienate your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于我們右邊的是本次游覽的亮點\N{\fs20}Coming up on our right is the highlight of our tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市政廳的驕傲\N{\fs20}The pride of city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stacey Paterno小姐\N{\fs20}Ms. Stacey Paterno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好美\N{\fs20}She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doug 你真煩人\N{\fs20}Doug, you're annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一眼都讓我反胃\N{\fs20}and the sight of you makes my stomach turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好\N{\fs20}Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doug 這位是我男朋友\N{\fs20}Doug, this is my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 還有你們 嗯\N{\fs20}Yeah, and you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不許看我的女人\N{\fs20}Better not be eyeballin' my woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 這位是Carter Heywood\N{\fs20}People, this is Carter Heywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個出柜的同性戀\N{\fs20}He's an avowed homosexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想騙我 真可恥\N{\fs20}Shame on you for trying to fool Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恥啊\N{\fs20}Shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我們往前\N{\fs20}And we're movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我們\N{\fs20}So, are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚還有戲嗎\N{\fs20}Still on for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 誰先走\N{\fs20}Yeah. Who leaves first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先 我出去的時候\N{\fs20}I will. On my way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會留一張合同在你桌上\N{\fs20}I'll drop a stack of contracts off on your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我十分鐘后裝作很惱火然后走吧\N{\fs20}Ok. Then you want me to act annoyed and leave 10 minutes later?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完成合同\N{\fs20}Oh, no. Finish the contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之后再去你家\N{\fs20}I'll swing by your house later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 Mike\N{\fs20}Hey, listen, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打我們在市長辦公室里的談話后\N{\fs20}Ever since we opened up to each other in the mayor's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都覺得我們的友誼上了一個新臺階\N{\fs20}I think we've taken our friendship to a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是的 Paul 那你現在可以閃人了嗎\N{\fs20}Me, too, Paul. Now you wanna get out of my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之呢 我家的事情有點棘手\N{\fs20}Anyway, listen. Things are a little tense at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貌似沒法讓Claudia懷上\N{\fs20}I just can't seem to get Claudia pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚 一夜又一夜\N{\fs20}Every night, night after night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在我背上 騎著我\N{\fs20}she's on my back, riding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到你的問題了\N{\fs20}I think I've zeroed in on your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道原因嗎 都是那些該死的懶精子 \N{\fs20}You know what it is? It's those damn lazy sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不會游泳\N{\fs20}They're just lousy swimmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們高臺跳水比賽時可以拿分呢\N{\fs20}Maybe they'll pick up points in the high dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不信\N{\fs20}And you can't believe the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些醫生怎么測試的 那個探針 哦喲\N{\fs20}tests the doctors gave me. The probing... ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這些個人隱私\N{\fs20}You just barrel ahead with the personal stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說是我睪丸的問題\N{\fs20}they figured out it was my testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stacey 紅色警報\N{\fs20}Stacey? Code red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paul 出去\N{\fs20}Paul, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你 能讓我在你辦公室工作 市長\N{\fs20}I appreciate you letting me work in your office, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道在外面干活多難\N{\fs20}You have no idea how hard it is to get any work done out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真同情你\N{\fs20}I totally empathize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候都不相信我在這兒的效率有那么低\N{\fs20}Sometimes I can't believe how little I get done in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊\N{\fs20}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥\N{\fs20}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒人來跟我閑聊\N{\fs20}No one ever just drops by to chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你貌似是個很好的聆聽者\N{\fs20}You seem like you're a pretty good listener.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我覺得我可是個帥小子\N{\fs20}Yeah, I think I'm a pretty good-looking kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 市長 我很樂意聊天 但是我實在是太忙了\N{\fs20}I'm sorry, sir, I would love to talk. It's just that I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望能安安靜靜的就好\N{\fs20}It's nice to have some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安安靜靜的\N{\fs20}Peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜\N{\fs20}Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜喲\N{\fs20}Silencio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 我能雇個實習生么\N{\fs20}Hey, Mike, can I hire an intern?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不行  - 別這樣Mike 我陷進去了\N{\fs20}- No. - Come on, Mike. I'm swamped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她多大了\N{\fs20}How old is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18 但你肯定會覺得她25了\N{\fs20}18, but you'd swear she's 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行\N{\fs20}No again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 明天我能晚來一點嗎\N{\fs20}Mike, can I come in late tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給一個肇事逃逸案件出庭作證\N{\fs20}I have to testify in a hit-and-run case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fs20}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 他是我一朋友\N{\fs20}No problem. I mean, he's a friend of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他已從昏迷中醒了\N{\fs20}but he's out of the coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記不記得你上次說行是什么時候\N{\fs20}Do you even remember the last time you said yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這工作讓你變冷血了\N{\fs20}I think this job might be making you a cold person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事兒\N{\fs20}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那昨天\N{\fs20}Uh-huh. And what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人問你要幾塊錢 你是怎么回答的\N{\fs20}when someone asked you for a few dollars yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不給 然后讓他自己去找份工作\N{\fs20}I said no and told him to get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 他才8歲\N{\fs20}Mike, he was 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他的游行樂隊賣糖果賺錢\N{\fs20}Selling candy bars for his marching band.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當什么啊 小孩一樣好騙嗎\N{\fs20}What was I, born yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要成為那種\N{\fs20}Do you wanna be the kind of guy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管別人問什么 總是說不的人么\N{\fs20}who automatically says no to people, no matter what the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 幫我個小忙\N{\fs20}Mike, quick favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能借用你的精子讓我老婆懷孕\N{\fs20}Can I use your sperm to impregnate my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行\N{\fs20}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 謝謝你 老兄\N{\fs20}Great. Thanks, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛說什么\N{\fs20}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是Stacey paterno\N{\fs20}This is Stacey paterno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doug 你過來一下\N{\fs20}Doug, get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們 如果你認真觀察\N{\fs20}Ladies and gentlemen, if you look closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會發現Doug很開心\N{\fs20}you can see Doug's elation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doug 你以后導游就別介紹我了\N{\fs20}Doug, I want off the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我明白你想要干什么\N{\fs20}Look, I understand what you're trying to do here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和我 我們沒可能的\N{\fs20}but you and I? We're just not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白么 我們不是一路人\N{\fs20}See, we're very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來自布魯克林的乖女孩兒\N{\fs20}I'm a simple girl from Brooklyn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡和自己的家人和朋友呆在一起\N{\fs20}who enjoys spending time with her family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個惱人的極品\N{\fs20}And you're an irritating freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs20}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 各位請繼續往這邊走\N{\fs20}Well, let's continue this way, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 嗯\N{\fs20}and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去時小心別踩著Doug破碎的心\N{\fs20}Try not to trample on Doug's broken heart as we walk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民朋友們好\N{\fs20}Why, hello there, citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 呵 呵 這就是市長\N{\fs20}Yeah, yeah, yeah. That's the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續走\N{\fs20}And we're movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看Mike 我已經給小家伙買了\N{\fs20}Look, Mike. I already got the little guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的第一個棒球手套\N{\fs20}his first baseball glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他是左撇子 商場促銷來著\N{\fs20}I hope he's a lefty. They were on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 有些事情我得跟你們說一下\N{\fs20}Uh, listen. There's something I... I have to tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有點難開口\N{\fs20}And it's a little difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直說了\N{\fs20}so I'm just gonna come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我說說 Nik\N{\fs20}Take it away, Nik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 各位\N{\fs20}Uh, look, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike還不想生一個孩子\N{\fs20}Mike just doesn't want to bring a child into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還和自己沒聯系\N{\fs20}without being involved in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 你要想介入就可以\N{\fs20}Mike, you can be involved as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 就你這么害怕承諾的人\N{\fs20}To tell you the truth, with your fear of commitment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得這對你來說是個好機會\N{\fs20}we thought this would be a perfect opportunity for you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來成為家庭一部分\N{\fs20}to be part of a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我不確定\N{\fs20}I... I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 我現在也有女朋友\N{\fs20}I mean, I'm in a relationship right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 說的好像能成似的\N{\fs20}Oh, yeah, like that's gonna work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我可以跟你們聊一下嗎\N{\fs20}Ok, can I talk to you guys for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我得跟你們清楚的解釋一下\N{\fs20}I think I need to explain this a little more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么人\N{\fs20}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看出我們的相似之處嗎\N{\fs20}Don't you see the resemblance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的微笑 色瞇瞇的眼神\N{\fs20}The winning smile? The bedroom eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的孩子\N{\fs20}You're my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴 是吧\N{\fs20}Not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這兒干嘛\N{\fs20}Wh-what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來道謝的\N{\fs20}I just came to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你 也就沒有我\N{\fs20}Without you, I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實不存在\N{\fs20}You don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合作一點吧 兄弟\N{\fs20}Work with me here, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在干一件偉大無私的事兒\N{\fs20}You're doing a great, selfless thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在干好事 對吧\N{\fs20}I am, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你明白了\N{\fs20}So, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike只是想等和他的真愛\N{\fs20}Mike just wants to wait and do this with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來完成這件事兒\N{\fs20}he's really in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是Mike\N{\fs20}Right, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia\N{\fs20}Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我參加\N{\fs20}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起生個孩子吧\N{\fs20}Let's make a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs20}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天 Mike\N{\fs20}Oh, my God, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 你愿意幫我生小孩兒我實在是太自豪了\N{\fs20}Mike, I can't tell you how proud I am that you're having my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 跟我說話 行嗎 怎么啦\N{\fs20}Nikki, talk to me, ok? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我男朋友就要搞大別人老婆的肚子了\N{\fs20}Oh, my boyfriend is impregnating another man's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 除此之外 還有其他煩心事么\N{\fs20}So, other than that, nothing's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大家要是知道這事兒了\N{\fs20}Do you know how awkward this is going to be for me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會多尷尬啊\N{\fs20}when people find out about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 你聽我說\N{\fs20}Nikki, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情我只想\N{\fs20}You are the only one I care enough about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你分享只關心你怎么想\N{\fs20}to have shared this information with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是副市長Mike Flaherty\N{\fs20}That's deputy mayor Mike Flaherty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把精子捐給了新聞發言人Paul Lassiter\N{\fs20}He's donating his sperm to press secretary Paul Lassiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki Nikki\N{\fs20}Nikki... Nikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就是本次觀光的亮點了\N{\fs20}And now, for the highlight of today's tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 又要來么\N{\fs20}Oh, great. Here we go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛非長這么漂亮\N{\fs20}Why do I have to be so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位\N{\fs20}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Janelle Cooper\N{\fs20}Is Janelle Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的生日是4月23號 金牛座\N{\fs20}She was born April 23, a Taurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感的代名詞\N{\fs20}Sign of the fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼\N{\fs20}Grrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Janelle 你竟然觀光介紹Janelle\N{\fs20}Janelle. You put Janelle on the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒沒什么可看的\N{\fs20}Nothing to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續往前走\N{\fs20}And we're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好 我好高興\N{\fs20}Well, good! I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興不用出現在你愚蠢的觀光介紹了\N{\fs20}I'm glad I'm off your stupid tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都在稱贊你\N{\fs20}Wow. People complimenting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你照相\N{\fs20}taking your picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你 你有多漂亮\N{\fs20}telling you you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有一天你覺得自己又丑又累\N{\fs20}Even on days when you're feeling ugly and tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有人來安慰你的\N{\fs20}people come by and make you feel all good about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人有病\N{\fs20}They're sick bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我們繼續往前\N{\fs20}And we're moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 Doug 我可是市長啊 天吶\N{\fs20}Come on, Doug. I'm the mayor, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 你能過來一下嗎\N{\fs20}Nikki? Could you come in here for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flaherty先生 我有點忙 有活干\N{\fs20}Actually, Mr. Flaherty, I'm a bit busy here, doing some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事是跟工作相關的\N{\fs20}This is work-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要討論籌款的計劃\N{\fs20}We're discussing fund-raising schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs20}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 在討論那事兒之前\N{\fs20}However, before we do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想花一點時間 談論一下\N{\fs20}I'd just like to take one moment to, uh, talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精子\N{\fs20}My sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說話經常都是這樣開頭的\N{\fs20}How many conversations have I started that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了\N{\fs20}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 聽著 大伙\N{\fs20}N-Nikki, look. Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事很好 這事兒我只有好處\N{\fs20}This is great. I mean, I get all the benefits of having a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何的壞處\N{\fs20}with none of the drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道大家都覺得Mike做的是對的嗎\N{\fs20}Don't you guys think that what Mike is doing is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 這一次我站在Mike這邊\N{\fs20}Actually, I'm with Mike on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 我會想要個孩子\N{\fs20}Someday, I'm gonna want to have a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要一些幫助\N{\fs20}and I'm gonna need some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一些卵子 一個子宮 一個胎盤\N{\fs20}I'm gonna need an egg, a uterus, a womb...
