Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 她配不上你嗎\N{\fs20}Why? She not good enough for ya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟你說了別穿紫色衣服\N{\fs20}I told ya not to wear the purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James在么\N{\fs20}James?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James在么\N{\fs20}James?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James 你在嗎\N{\fs20}James, you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是大轉盤時間了\N{\fs20}It's wheel time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線索是 它是一項活動\N{\fs20}The clue is... It's an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我覺得是土撥鼠日\N{\fs20}I... I'm thinking groundhog day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者割禮\N{\fs20}or a bris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你\N{\fs20}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子\N{\fs20}It's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還跟我愛的女人在一起\N{\fs20}And you're here with the woman I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么征兆嗎\N{\fs20}Is this some kind of sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 這位是Bobby Hamilton\N{\fs20}Uh, Mike, this is Bobby Hamilton,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會計部Gary Hamilton的兒子\N{\fs20}son of Gary Hamilton in accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先走了\N{\fs20}I'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人嚇屎我了\N{\fs20}That man is scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粑粑\N{\fs20}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎 Mike\N{\fs20}You ok, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 說這么多關于孩子的事兒\N{\fs20}Yeah. You know, all this talk about babies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我有點激動呢\N{\fs20}it's getting me kinda worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是提醒我 我們下周一起\N{\fs20}Which reminds me, let's have dinner next week
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的朋友Jeff Lyles和他老婆吃頓飯\N{\fs20}with my friend Jeff Lyles and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會喜歡她的\N{\fs20}You'll like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個瑞典人\N{\fs20}She's swedish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂一點法語\N{\fs20}I know a little French.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就去造人吧\N{\fs20}Let's... let's go make a baby right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 我服過避孕藥了\N{\fs20}Mike, I'm on the pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我這不是情緒上來了么 我又不是白癡\N{\fs20}I know. I'm caught up in the moment. I'm not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想要你 就在這兒\N{\fs20}I want you right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fs20}Take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個好上了嗎\N{\fs20}Are you guys dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從耶魯畢業后 我在市議會贏得議席\N{\fs20}After Yale, I won my first elected office in the city council,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后做了6年清貧的區長后\N{\fs20}and after a 6-year stint as borough president,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就成了這座偉大城市的市長\N{\fs20}I became the mayor of this great city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我只是覺得\N{\fs20}I don't know. I just don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不適合做市政廳游覽的講解材料\N{\fs20}you're city hall tour material.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以炒了你\N{\fs20}I can also get you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎\N{\fs20}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很確定哦\N{\fs20}I'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 Doug看明白了\N{\fs20}Well, Doug sees your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要搬家\N{\fs20}And I'm moving.
